member_experience_collection.title: Senior Graphic Designer
member_experience_collection.description: Design seasonal Print and Graphics for Kid Boy and Toddler Boy including sleep and underwear. Manage Freelance and Associate design members. Develop graphic point of view per season. Create production files and insure timely and complete hand off to vendor. Input production codes into corporate database systems for vendors. Collaborate with VP and Senior Design Directors to establish seasonal concept direction

member_experience_collection.title: Freelance Graphic Designer
member_experience_collection.description: Design freehand distressed fashion graphics for Aeropostale's women’s casual wear; deliver production-ready files in a deadline-driven environment. Combine embroidery with antique styled thematic designs for their  Times Square flagship store. Incorporate company branding logo within designs.

member_experience_collection.title: Freelance Graphic Designer
member_experience_collection.description: Design freehand illustrations and fashion graphics for Old Navy men’s and women’s casual wear; deliver production-ready files in a deadline-driven environment. Conduct research on seasonal images and trends; establish thematic design elements in collaboration with senior designer. Incorporate company branding logo within designs.

member_experience_collection.title: Lead Designer
member_experience_collection.description: Manage internal company graphics and designs, including Web site, marketing collateral, showroom graphics, advertising, and signage; create impactful tradeshow exhibits. Communicate design concepts to clients, including Charles Schwab and NEC. Ensure exhibit designs reflect client style preferences and business needs. Collaborate with peers on projects; inform parent company on design-related issues. Trained new employees on hardware and software applications.

member_experience_collection.title: In-House Designer
member_experience_collection.description:
Spearheaded company and artist branding and visual direction for established music company; created album and Web design, branding, e-commerce implementation, and advertising. Served as liaison between musicians and managers to communicate overall design themes. Provided branding support for offshoot labels and associated clubs and events.
Effectively established a vibrant Web presence through the design and launch of the first company Web site.
